Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,獸之呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,柒之型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,空間視覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,對 在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到對方強到不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你真厲害伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要先解決這些傢伙 否則沒辦法向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,難道沒有甚麽好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,—————————OP—————————
